that was a bit Of a cheat.

37:19.779 --> 37:20.939
That day isn't coming.

37:21.114 --> 37:22.445
It's now.

37:23.158 --> 37:25.774
The way I calculate it,
we can all starve,

37:25.952 --> 37:27.943
or with proper rationing
and cultivation,

37:28.121 --> 37:30.112
three-quarters of us can survive.

37:31.416 --> 37:33.873
And how do you propose tO do that?

37:34.794 --> 37:36.079
Shake the tree?

37:37.464 --> 37:39.671
You could use the information
we gathered today

37:39.841 --> 37:42.583
tO determine who's an asset
and who's a burden.

37:43.052 --> 37:45.668
Those hard choices could be made,
but not by me.

37:46.848 --> 37:49.089
Dome chose you to make them.

37:50.351 --> 37:52.012
And you've gotta do it now.

37:52.187 --> 37:54.394
Before it's tOO late.

37:58.276 --> 37:59.311
[METAL CLAN KS]

37:59.486 --> 38:00.646
LYLE:
Hey!

38:00.820 --> 38:02.560
Man.

38:03.531 --> 38:04.862
We need tO talk.

38:06.075 --> 38:07.326
I guess you found out.

38:07.494 --> 38:08.984
That my mother's alive?

38:11.164 --> 38:12.825
She told me you'd have answers.

38:13.708 --> 38:15.619
TO some pretty provocative
quesﬂons.

38:16.169 --> 38:17.659
DO you know who killed Angie?

38:22.008 --> 38:23.043
