38:23.218 --> 38:25.834
IS that what you and my uncle
were talking about?

38:26.346 --> 38:28.962
Hey, I need you to tell me
everything!

38:31.392 --> 38:33.303
I can dO that.

38:34.854 --> 38:37.561
Provided you give consideration
tO my needs.

38:40.443 --> 38:42.820
- Which are?
- You let me out Of here.

38:45.156 --> 38:47.863
I'll give you an all-access pass.

38:51.371 --> 38:54.113
What do you say, James?

38:55.500 --> 38:58.788
- What was the locker number again?
- Eighteen-twenty—one.

38:58.962 --> 38:59.997
Here we gO.

39:00.171 --> 39:02.708
People who have had that locker
over the last 50 years.

39:02.882 --> 39:04.873
Okay, what exactly
are we looking for?

39:05.051 --> 39:06.882
Anything tO jog her memory.

39:11.182 --> 39:12.683
GIRL:
Wait.

39:13.142 --> 39:16.430
Melanie Cross?
That looks familiar tO you?

39:16.604 --> 39:18.185
GIRL:
Something about it.

39:18.356 --> 39:20.267
1988.

39:21.234 --> 39:23.850
I'll pull the yearbook from that year.

39:30.869 --> 39:32.450
Brazier.

39:32.620 --> 39:34.030
Connor.

